text: Don’t buy! This phone case started peeling after a week and the buttons barely work. Super disappointed, not worth it at all.

text: Product is fine, does what it says, but came in like three layers of plastic and a giant box. Not eco-friendly at all.

text: Hands down my favorite thing I bought in months. Super easy to use, feels premium, and works exactly as described. 10/10 would recommend.

text: Got this for my sister’s birthday and she absolutely loved it!! It came wrapped nicely and works just as described. Would recommend for anyone who likes cute gadgets.

text: It’s not bad, it’s not amazing. Just okay for the price. Does the job, but don’t expect anything fancy. Kinda wish I spent a bit more for a nicer model.

text: Sound quality is pretty good, and they’re comfortable for long calls. The mic is just okay, sometimes people say I sound muffled. Otherwise, no complaints.

text: Didn’t think my lazy cat would be interested, but he goes wild for this toy. If you have a picky feline, this is a must. Batteries last a long time, too.

text: I struggle finding chargers that work with my chunky phone case. This cable is long enough and fits just fine. Charges fast too. Solid purchase.

text: Not bad, but kinda flimsy for what it costs. The setup was easy, but it doesn’t feel super premium. It works though, so keeping it for now.

text: The listing said it had a metal base but it’s just plastic. Feels cheap and unstable. Wouldn’t buy again, honestly pretty bummed.

text: I barely used this once and it just snapped in half. Super disappointed. Contacted support but haven’t heard back yet. Would not recommend.

text: Used this on my recent trip and it held up great. Lightweight, durable, and the zipper didn’t snag once. Wish I bought one sooner!

title: Love the design!
text: I’ve gotten so many compliments since I started using this bag. The pattern is fun and it’s got plenty of pockets. Would totally get another one.

text: You get what you pay for. Not the best, not the worst. It does the job but I wouldn’t expect it to last for years or anything.

text: Honestly, I was expecting a bit more based on the photos, but it's still nice. The color is spot on and it fits me okay, but the fabric is a little thinner than I thought it would be. Wore it a couple times and got compliments tho! Just wish it was a tad thicker, especially for fall weather. Overall not bad and shipping was super quick.

title: Super comfy

title: Not what I was hoping for
text: Meh, didn't really work out. The straps are awkward and the sizing felt off, way too tight around the waist and loose at the top. Also the zipper got stuck the first time I tried it on, which was super annoying. Sent it back the next day. Wouldn't recommend if you have a bigger bust.
